FBIS3-21802 "jptdd011__l94014" JPRS-TDD-94-011-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Narcotics 14 March 1994 LATIN AMERICA BOLIVIA Seleme, Former Officials Summoned by Santa Cruz Special Antinarcotics Force PY0503134294 La Paz Radio Fides Network in Spanish 1100 GMT 5 Mar 94 PY0503134294 La Paz Radio Fides Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] In a seemingly all-out war waged by the national government, the Santa Cruz Special Antinarcotics Force has summoned Susana Seleme, a former secretary to the president of the Republic [Jaime Paz Zamora]; Rolando Arostegui, a former Santa Cruz mayor under the Patriotic Accord administration; Carlos Valverde, a former Interior Ministry intelligence department chief and a former assistant to [former Interior Minister] Guillermo Capobianco; Orlando Elmer Saucedo, the Interior Ministry seizures department chief during Capobianco's tenure; and other officials whose names we were unable to obtain.
